race.comment: MODEST MAN (3) has an excellent record over this course and distance having never missed the placings in four starts, including two wins and two placings. Hit the frame latest (29.97) when second at this track in a Grade 5. Rates a leading player. BEES HIVE (5) was crowded for room and fell at Gosford last time after finishing fifth in a Grade 5 two back. Rates a leading chance on best. RAINBOW BLUE (1) stuck on well last time to finish 0.8 lengths back in third (23.00) at Maitland in a Grade 5 over 400m. Good beginner assisted by the inside draw. Can feature again. PITMAN GO QUICK (2) is a last-start placegetter who will have admirers.
